## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "Word to PDF/Text Converter" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

Word to PDF/Text Converter offers a range of features to enhance your Language Translation and Learning experience. Explore the following capabilities:

### customization of PDF

Word to PDF/Text Converter have several customatization features like font size from 8 to 24, different font families and Words Per Page( WPP ) of PDF to define on your own. Also, in font family, you have different options to define different Languages.

### Word to Text

Now you can convert Word to Text and copy, paste in anywhere. 

### Word to PDF

All you need to Pick the Word from the files that you want to convert into PDF, Customize different options and convert it. It is fast and accurate. By default, it will store in your application directory under Files. 

